    <title>NVIDIA Jetson Nano 部署 ZLMediaKit</title>
    <url>/2022/09/15/NVIDIA%20Jetson%20Nano%20%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%20ZLMediaKit/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>主要介绍如何在NVIDIA Jetson Nano 部署 ZLMediaKit。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h1><p><a href="https://gitee.com/xia-chu/ZLMediaKit">gitee.com</a></p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/ZLMediaKit/ZLMediaKit/wiki/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B">github.com</a></p>
<h1 id="本机环境"><a href="#本机环境" class="headerlink" title="本机环境"></a>本机环境</h1><p><img src="https://res.craft.do/user/full/7000ef9f-cc11-00bc-0790-dd58dd9cbf19/doc/1c852e54-7d06-4de9-860a-7b44463babf9/855dd04d-b878-41c7-b2a0-231855e8734e" alt="image.png"></p>
<h1 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h1><h2 id="下载项目"><a href="#下载项目" class="headerlink" title="下载项目"></a>下载项目</h2><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone <span class="operator">--</span>depth <span class="number">1</span> https:<span class="comment">//gitee.com/xia-chu/ZLMediaKit</span></span><br><span class="line">cd <span class="type">ZLMediaKit</span><span class="operator">/</span></span><br><span class="line">git submodule update <span class="operator">--</span><span class="keyword">init</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="安装依赖库"><a href="#安装依赖库" class="headerlink" title="安装依赖库"></a>安装依赖库</h2><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#除了openssl,其他其实都可以不安装</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt<span class="operator">-</span><span class="keyword">get</span> install libssl<span class="operator">-</span>dev</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt<span class="operator">-</span><span class="keyword">get</span> install libsdl<span class="operator">-</span>dev</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt<span class="operator">-</span><span class="keyword">get</span> install libavcodec<span class="operator">-</span>dev</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt<span class="operator">-</span><span class="keyword">get</span> install libavutil<span class="operator">-</span>dev</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt<span class="operator">-</span><span class="keyword">get</span> install ffmpeg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="构建和编译项目"><a href="#构建和编译项目" class="headerlink" title="构建和编译项目"></a>构建和编译项目</h2><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd <span class="type">ZLMediaKit</span></span><br><span class="line">mkdir build</span><br><span class="line">cd build</span><br><span class="line">cmake <span class="operator">..</span></span><br><span class="line">make <span class="operator">-</span>j4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="运行"><a href="#运行" class="headerlink" title="运行"></a>运行</h2><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd <span class="type">ZLMediaKit</span><span class="operator">/</span>release<span class="operator">/</span>linux<span class="operator">/</span><span class="type">Debug</span></span><br><span class="line">#通过<span class="operator">-</span>h可以了解启动参数</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">./</span><span class="type">MediaServer</span> <span class="operator">-</span>h</span><br><span class="line">#以守护进程模式启动</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">./</span><span class="type">MediaServer</span> <span class="operator">-</span>d <span class="operator">&amp;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://res.craft.do/user/full/7000ef9f-cc11-00bc-0790-dd58dd9cbf19/doc/1c852e54-7d06-4de9-860a-7b44463babf9/b5ff5fe6-2b93-43c6-aca8-55774b6c3ae5" alt="image.png"></p>
]]></content>
